t still feels lost after reading it, this task is not done.","created_at":"2026-03-21T23:38:16Z"},{"id":352,"issue_id":"bd-j9jo3.6.1","author":"ubuntu","text":"Sensitivity follow-up: snapshot must surface disclosure-control markers and safe-preview semantics clearly enough that a first-contact agent understands when evidence is present but transformed, rather than mistaking redaction for missing data.","created_at":"2026-03-22T01:37:21Z"}]}
 {"id":"bd-j9jo3.6.2","title":"robot-redesign/surfaces: rewrite status as a cheap summary surface","description":"Rewrite --robot-status so it is explicitly the cheap summary surface rather than a fuzzy alternative bootstrap entrypoint. This task exists to preserve a fast low-token health glance without repeating snapshot's full responsibility.","design":"The new status surface should present a compact summary derived from the shared runtime projection, with stable semantics around freshness and degraded state, and without silently omitting context in ways that mislead consumers into thinking they saw the whole world.\\n\\nThe design should make the relationship between status and snapshot obvious and intentional.","acceptance_criteria":"This task is complete when status is faster, smaller, and semantically narrower than snapshot while still remaining trustworthy and useful for quick polling and shell automation.","notes":"Status should be easy to depend on precisely because it tries to do less.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","estimated_minutes":150,"created_at":"2026-03-21T23:38:16.508210049Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-03-22T23:06:56.346956002Z","closed_at":"2026-03-22T23:06:56.346419808Z","close_reason":"Projection-backed --robot-status is now the cheap summary surface with schema_id, source health section, bounded live fallback, REST parity, and targeted robot/serve verification.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["robot-redesign","status","surfaces"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-j9jo3.6.2","depends_on_id":"bd-j9jo3.1.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-21T23:40:02.833439859Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-j9jo3.6.2","depends_on_id":"bd-j9jo3.1.5","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-03-21T23:47:58.005678859Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-j9jo3.6.2","depends_on_id":"bd-j9jo3.1.6","type":"blocks","created_at":"